{"article_id":"v4Lb8R0NFdEFR9gl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"National Security Adviser Michael Flynn discussed U.S. sanctions against Russia with the Russian ambassador","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"before President Trump took office ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"according to new reports","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"that prompted the top Democrat on the House Foreign Affairs Committee to call for Mr. Flynn ' s immediate firing .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Mr. Flynn denied","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"he had discussed the sanctions with Ambassador Sergey Kislyak to The Washington Post on Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"before a spokesman said Thursday","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"while Mr. Flynn had no recollection","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"of discussing sanctions ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"he \" couldn ' t be certain \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that the topic never came up .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"The Post said","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"its report relied on \" nine current and former officials \"","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"who were in senior positions at multiple agencies at the time of the calls .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Mr. Trump told reporters aboard Air Force One Friday","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"that he hadn ' t seen the report ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"but that he ' d \" look into that . \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Former President Barack Obama ' s administration slapped new sanctions on Russian officials in December in response to alleged Russian interference in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"If Mr. Flynn did discuss sanctions with the Russian ambassador ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"that would contradict what the administration ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"including Vice President Mike Pence ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"has said about those talks .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Before Mr. Trump was sworn in ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"current White House press secretary Sean Spicer said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Flynn had contacted Mr. Kislyak on Dec. 25","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to wish him a merry Christmas","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and then several days later","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to discuss logistics","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"about setting up a phone call between Mr. Trump and Russian President Vladimir Putin","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"once Mr. Trump took office .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"The sanctions","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"imposed by the Obama administration","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"were announced on Dec. 29 .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Pence told CBS News last month","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that the conversations did not deal with the United States ' decision","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to expel diplomats","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"or impose censure against Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"he had talked to Mr. Flynn about the matter .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"A Trump administration official \" stressed","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that Pence made his comments","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"based on his conversation with Flynn , \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The Post report said .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Rep. Eliot Engel , ranking member on the House Foreign Affairs Committee , said","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Trump \" must relieve General Flynn immediately . \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" Either General Flynn lied to the administration","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"or the administration lied to the American people , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"said Mr. Engel , New York Democrat .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"\" In any case , the administration ' s sloppy handling of such a serious issue creates a threat smack in the middle of our national security apparatus . \"","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff , the ranking member on the House intelligence committee , said","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"the allegation","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that Mr. Flynn \" secretly discussed \" ways","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"to \" undermine \" the sanctions","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"while Mr. Obama was still in office","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"\" raises serous questions of legality and fitness for office . \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"\" If he did so ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and then he and other administration officials misled the American people ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"his conduct would be all the more pernicious ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and he should no longer serve in this administration or any other , \"","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"said Mr. Schiff , California Democrat .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Sen. Mike Rounds , South Dakota Republican , said","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"it would be up to Mr. Trump to dole out any potential punishment","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"and that he ' s giving the current administration the benefit of the doubt at this point .","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"The National Security Adviser is not a position","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"that requires Senate confirmation .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"the first thing","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"we ' ll do","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"is get all the facts , \"","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Rounds said on CNN Friday .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"\" And then","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"if the facts lead us in the direction","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that say","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that we ' ve been misled","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"or that there ' s been misinformation provided ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"he ' s an employee of the president .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"We would expect the president to take appropriate actions , \"","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"\" If there needs to be discussions within Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that ' ll happen .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"But the president is in charge of his employees","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and I think","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and I ' m going to give him the benefit of the doubt on this -","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"he ' ll act appropriately at the appropriate time with full facts , \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Mr. Rounds said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":175,"left":105,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":91,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":89,"right":90,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":92,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":6,"right":96,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":7,"right":95,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":12,"right":99,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":15,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":147,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":109,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","